.cache/
.test-corpus/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
# Glob `output/*` (not `output/`) so individual file `!` exceptions
# below take effect — git ignores the entire directory when the
# pattern matches the directory itself, regardless of `!file`
# negations underneath.
output/*
# Evidence file backing `HEURISTIC_RULE_AXIS_CAP` in
# `crates/engine/src/engine.rs` (issue #133 PR 4). Committed as the
# audit trail for the cap value — re-runs of `--mode heuristic-frequency`
# overwrite this file and any number drift would surface as a diff.
!output/heuristic_frequencies.json
!output/heuristic_frequencies.json.license
